<p>The basic transliteration model would neglect these characters
producing erroneous mixed-tokensâ€” that is, words between English and Al Bhed. 
Engbhed?  Here are the same words as above without considering diacritics.</p>

<ul>
  <li>*dÃªda-Ã -dÃªda</li>
  <li>*nÃ©cisÃ©</li>
  <li>*zymybaÃ±u</li>
</ul>

<p>Since itâ€™s unknown whether these diacritics have usage in Al Bhed, by default
these diacritics are removed to reflect a more <em>standard</em> English. 
However, diacritics can be maintained by passing <code class="highlighter-rouge">--allow_diacritics=True</code>.</p>

